Yomi Casual and his wife Grace are celebrating their wedding anniversary today and the fashion designer took to Instagram to express his love for his wife.

The couple has been married for 3 years and has been together for way longer. The union has produced two children, a girl and a boy.

Sharing a photo of them together, Yomi wrote: “How is it that I can still get goosebumps when I see your beautiful face after 9years? Happy wedding Anniversary to my amazing wife, no years can erase the special feeling I have when you walk into room.”

“I still get goosebumps when I see your face even after 9 years” Yomi Casual writes as he and wife Grace celebrate wedding anniversary

